result.notes:
Counts (in cells per litre) of potentially Toxic Algal cells for the Food 
Standards Agency (FSA). These data are from samples collected from shellfish 
beds around the coast of England and Wales from 1996 to the present. Summary 
data from 2012 is published on the FSA website 
`http://www.food.gov.uk/enforcement/monitoring/shellfish/ewbiotoxin/`_
